content: This game is absolutely delightful; a real joy to play. Developer is very helpful. On my device (Sony Xperia Tablet Z), there is a problem with the driver on the graphics processor that causes the game to crash frequently. Devices with this processor are the only ones that have this problem, and it's out of the developer's hands. Check your graphics processor before downloading and don't rate based on that glitch! Crashing is minimized by staying out of the field directly in front of the house, and is rare in other fields.
